In mathematics, the '''Dieudonné plank''' is a specific [[topological space]] introduced by {{harvs|txt|last=Dieudonné|year=1944|authorlink=Jean Dieudonné}}. It is an example of a [[metacompact space]] that is not [[paracompact space|paracompact]].

